Title: AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF A BARRIO IN THE MUNICIPALITY OF BAUAN, PROVINCE OF BATANGAS, FROM CALACA TO RIZAL.
Data:
[ Act No. 3934, November 29, 1932 ]
AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF A BARRIO IN THE MUNICIPALITY OF BAUAN, PROVINCE OF BATANGAS, FROM CALACA TO RIZAL.
Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives of the Philippines in Legislature assembled and by the authority of the same:
Section 1. The name of the barrio of Calaca, in the municipality of Bauan, Province of Batangas, to all intents and purposes, shall hereafter be known as Rizal.1a—àphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect on its approval.
Approved, November 29, 1932.
